data.description: What a gem! It's hard to find a four bedroom, two bath home for this price that is this nice! Located just minutes away from the University of South Alabama, local hospitals and central to almost everything Mobile has to offer. This home has vinyl plank floors running throughout and updated lighting fixtures. The living and finding room flows together and the kitchen has painted cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The water heater is a gas tankless Rinnai unit. The oversized primary bedroom and bathroom offers plenty of space, with the additional bedrooms being a good size as well. The backyard is flat, and has mature landscaping and a privacy fence. Don't miss out on this one! All measurements are approximate and not guaranteed, buyer to verify.
